{"type": "article", "id": 19333, "title": "黄铜烛台", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607120127knMp3rUCJ6zlgQKG.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个黄铜制作的烛台，来自瑞典皇室品牌 Skultuna。烛台的形状源于 Skultuna 有着 408 岁的铸造厂，经历过多次大火摧毁和重建，有着特别的纪念意义。烛台的底座是方形的，四面的形状并不相同，表面的镂空窗户让它显得精致而有层次感。有 8.5 厘米高，可经水洗，售价 69 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.finnishdesignshop.com/decoration-candleholders-skultuna-the-factory-the-factory-candleholder-brass-p-11131.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614584894zncuDLi7jUpeQk.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145849knWiKp1gcB9wh0bF.jpg\" width=\"415\" height=\"279\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67228916\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145849cD6OPGxnvQLISApW.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}